{
  "name": "GitHub Radar — gharchive Discovery (ISI-955)",
  "type": "dashboard",
  "content": {
    "version": 21,
    "variables": [],
    "tiles": {
      "0": {
        "type": "markdown",
        "title": "GitHub Radar — Discovery Pipeline (gharchive)",
        "content": "# GitHub Radar — Discovery Pipeline\n\nMonitors the gharchive event-stream discovery source introduced in ISI-950 (Path C). Live metric emission is wired in ISI-955 hooks (`internal/daemon/gharchive_discovery_hooks.go`).\n\n**Current health gates** (from ISI-950 acceptance):\n\n- Active repo count ≥ 5000 after 7-day soak\n- Classifier queue depth bounded\n- Live GitHub API rate-limit usage < 80%\n- Dedup working (ratio > 0.9 steady state)\n\n**Phase B telemetry coverage (this dashboard rev):**\n\n| Tile | Series wired? | Gated on |\n|------|---|---|\n| Archive ingest lag | ✅ | merged + redeployed |\n| Events processed | ⚠️ scalar `event_type=unknown` | ISI-961 (per-type hook signature) |\n| Candidates per hour | ✅ | ISI-1005 pipeline hooks |\n| Dedup ratio | ✅ | ISI-1005 pipeline hooks |\n| Classifier queue depth | ❌ | ISI-954 backpressure-gate code |\n\nOwner: Observability Agent · Story: ISI-955 · Pipeline hooks: ISI-1005 · Soak: ISI-956"
      },
      "1": {
        "type": "data",
        "title": "Archive ingest lag (seconds)",
        "query": "timeseries lag = avg(github_radar.discovery.gharchive.lag_seconds), interval: 5m",
        "visualization": "lineChart",
        "visualizationSettings": {
          "thresholds": [
            {
              "id": 0,
              "field": "lag",
              "isEnabled": true,
              "rules": [
                { "value": 3600, "color": { "Default": "var(--dt-colors-charts-warning-default)" } },
                { "value": 14400, "color": { "Default": "var(--dt-colors-charts-critical-default)" } }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "chartSettings": {
            "gapPolicy": "gap",
            "circleChartSettings": { "groupingThresholdType": "relative", "groupingThresholdValue": 0, "valueType": "relative" },
            "categoryOverrides": {},
            "fieldMapping": { "timestamp": "timeframe", "leftAxisValues": ["lag"], "leftAxisDimensions": [], "fields": [], "values": [] }
          },
          "singleValue": { "showLabel": true, "label": "Latest lag (s)", "prefixIcon": "", "recordField": "lag" },
          "table": { "rowDensity": "condensed", "enableSparklines": false, "hiddenColumns": [], "lineWrapIds": [], "columnWidths": {} }
        },
        "querySettings": { "maxResultRecords": 1000, "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1, "defaultSamplingRatio": 10, "enableSampling": false }
      },
      "2": {
        "type": "data",
        "title": "Events processed (gharchive)",
        "query": "timeseries events = sum(github_radar.discovery.gharchive.events_processed_total), interval: 5m, by: { event_type }",
        "visualization": "areaChart",
        "visualizationSettings": {
          "chartSettings": {
            "gapPolicy": "gap",
            "categoryOverrides": {},
            "fieldMapping": { "timestamp": "timeframe", "leftAxisValues": ["events"], "leftAxisDimensions": ["event_type"], "fields": [], "values": [] }
          },
          "singleValue": { "showLabel": true, "label": "Events", "prefixIcon": "", "recordField": "events" },
          "table": { "rowDensity": "condensed", "enableSparklines": false, "hiddenColumns": [], "lineWrapIds": [], "columnWidths": {} }
        },
        "querySettings": { "maxResultRecords": 1000, "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1, "defaultSamplingRatio": 10, "enableSampling": false }
      },
      "3": {
        "type": "data",
        "title": "Candidates per hour (gharchive)",
        "query": "timeseries candidates = sum(github_radar.discovery.gharchive.candidates_total), interval: 5m, by: { event_type }",
        "visualization": "barChart",
        "visualizationSettings": {
          "chartSettings": {
            "gapPolicy": "gap",
            "categoryOverrides": {},
            "fieldMapping": { "timestamp": "timeframe", "leftAxisValues": ["candidates"], "leftAxisDimensions": ["event_type"], "fields": [], "values": [] }
          },
          "singleValue": { "showLabel": true, "label": "Candidates", "prefixIcon": "", "recordField": "candidates" },
          "table": { "rowDensity": "condensed", "enableSparklines": false, "hiddenColumns": [], "lineWrapIds": [], "columnWidths": {} }
        },
        "querySettings": { "maxResultRecords": 1000, "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1, "defaultSamplingRatio": 10, "enableSampling": false }
      },
      "4": {
        "type": "data",
        "title": "Dedup ratio (gharchive)",
        "query": "timeseries dedup = avg(github_radar.discovery.gharchive.dedup_ratio), interval: 5m",
        "visualization": "lineChart",
        "visualizationSettings": {
          "thresholds": [
            {
              "id": 0,
              "field": "dedup",
              "isEnabled": true,
              "rules": [
                { "value": 0.5, "color": { "Default": "var(--dt-colors-charts-warning-default)" } },
                { "value": 0.9, "color": { "Default": "var(--dt-colors-charts-critical-default)" } }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "chartSettings": {
            "gapPolicy": "gap",
            "circleChartSettings": { "groupingThresholdType": "relative", "groupingThresholdValue": 0, "valueType": "relative" },
            "categoryOverrides": {},
            "fieldMapping": { "timestamp": "timeframe", "leftAxisValues": ["dedup"], "leftAxisDimensions": [], "fields": [], "values": [] }
          },
          "singleValue": { "showLabel": true, "label": "Dedup ratio", "prefixIcon": "", "recordField": "dedup" },
          "table": { "rowDensity": "condensed", "enableSparklines": false, "hiddenColumns": [], "lineWrapIds": [], "columnWidths": {} }
        },
        "querySettings": { "maxResultRecords": 1000, "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1, "defaultSamplingRatio": 10, "enableSampling": false }
      },
      "5": {
        "type": "markdown",
        "title": "Pending tiles — wiring gaps",
        "content": "### Tiles pending engineering merges\n\n- **Classifier queue depth** — wait on ISI-954 (`gharchive_backpressure` branch not yet merged). Named series:\n  - `github_radar.discovery.classifier.queue_depth`\n- **Per-event-type breakdown** on the *Events processed* tile — wait on ISI-961 (keptPerType hook signature). Until merged the tile renders a single `event_type=unknown` row.\n\n**Wired in this dashboard rev (ISI-1005):**\n\n- **Candidates per hour** — `candidates_total` counter emitted per admitted candidate via pipeline hooks.\n- **Dedup ratio** — `dedup_ratio` gauge emitted after each dedup pass.\n\nInstrument registry lives in `internal/metrics/discovery_meters.go`."
      }
    },
    "layouts": {
      "0": { "x": 0,  "y": 0,  "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "1": { "x": 0,  "y": 4,  "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "2": { "x": 12, "y": 4,  "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "3": { "x": 0,  "y": 12, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "4": { "x": 12, "y": 12, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "5": { "x": 0,  "y": 20, "w": 24, "h": 4 }
    },
    "settings": {
      "gridLayout": { "columnsCount": 24 }
    }
  }
}
